text: Guzal Yusupova (; born 19 December 1997) is an Uzbekistani tennis player. Yusupova has a career high WTA singles ranking of 746 achieved on 8 September 2014. She also has a career high WTA doubles ranking of 697 achieved on 18 August 2014. Yusupova made her WTA main draw debut at the 2013 Tashkent Open in the doubles draw partnering Arina Folts. == External links == * * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Uzbekistani female tennis players Category:People from Qashqadaryo Region
